#: ../nethsm/administration.rst:109
msgid "*Provisioned*"
msgstr "*Provisioned*"

#: ../nethsm/administration.rst:109
msgid ""
"NetHSM with configuration. The *Provisioned* state implies either "
"*Operational* or *Locked* state."
msgstr ""
"NetHSM s konfigurací. Stav *Provisioned* znamená buď stav *Operational*, "
"nebo *Locked*."

#: ../nethsm/administration.rst:112
msgid "*Operational*"
msgstr "*Provozní*"

#: ../nethsm/administration.rst:112
msgid ""
"NetHSM with configuration and ready to execute commands. The "
"*Operational* state implies the *Provisioned* state."
msgstr ""
"NetHSM s konfigurací a připravený k provádění příkazů. Stav *Operational*"
" znamená stav *Provisioned*."

#: ../nethsm/administration.rst:115
msgid "*Locked*"
msgstr "*Zamčeno*"

#: ../nethsm/administration.rst:115
msgid ""
